From:

Cc: 
Subject: Epstein 
Hi and I are the supervisors of the Public Corruption Unit in the Southern District of New York, and we 
understand you reached out to one of the line AUSAs in our unit, S regarding our Epstein investigation. We 
wanted to introduce ourselves and connect. Do you have time for a call tomorrow or Monday? 
Thanks, 
Deputy Chief, Public Corruption Unit 
U.S. Attorney's Office for the 
Southern District of New York 
EFTA00027046
